" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:shape:options:"},{"type":"text","text":". Alternatively, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:features:options:"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:shapes:options:"},{"type":"text","text":" method to create a shape source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with an array. "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource\/initWithIdentifier:features:options:"},{"type":"text","text":" accepts only "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances, such as "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointFeature"},{"type":"text","text":" objects, whose attributes you can use when"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"applying a predicate to "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":" or configuring a style layer’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"appearance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Extracting GeoJSON data from the map","anchor":"Extracting-GeoJSON-data-from-the-map","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Any ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","isActive":true},{"text":", or ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollectionFeature","isActive":true},{"text":" object has an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape\/geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","isActive":true},{"text":" method that you can use to create a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"GeoJSON source code representation of the object. You can extract a feature","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object from the map using a method such as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/visibleFeaturesAtPoint:","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"About GeoJSON deserialization","anchor":"About-GeoJSON-deserialization","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The process of converting GeoJSON text into "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":", or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollectionFeature","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects is known as “GeoJSON deserialization”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON geometries, features, and feature collections are known in this SDK as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shapes, features, and shape collection features, respectively."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Each GeoJSON object ty